  "page": "Dake",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the guard of House Lannister, see <a href=\"/index.php/Dake_(guard)\" title=\"Dake (guard)\">Dake (guard)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Dake</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Dake_TSS_Comic.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Dake TSS Comic.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7a/Dake_TSS_Comic.jpg/300px-Dake_TSS_Comic.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"280\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7a/Dake_TSS_Comic.jpg/450px-Dake_TSS_Comic.jpg 1.5x, /images/7/7a/Dake_TSS_Comic.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Dake by Mike S Miller for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> <a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">graphic novel</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Osgrey\" title=\"House Osgrey\">House Osgrey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dake</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Peasant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Peasant\">peasant</a> who served <a href=\"/index.php/House_Osgrey\" title=\"House Osgrey\">House Osgrey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After being trained by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Eustace_Osgrey\" title=\"Eustace Osgrey\">Eustace Osgrey</a>'s sons with other peasants, Dake went off to fight for <a href=\"/index.php/House_Osgrey\" title=\"House Osgrey\">House Osgrey</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"First Blackfyre Rebellion\">First Blackfyre Rebellion</a>. Eustace considered him to be an expert forager, and Dake was able enough to provide for the whole group as they marched. Dake was one of the only three surviving men that returned with Ser Eustace, along with <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_(Standfast)\" title=\"Pate (Standfast)\">Pate</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lem_(Standfast)\" title=\"Lem (Standfast)\">Lem</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Years later, Dake was accused of stealing sheep by members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Webber\" title=\"House Webber\">House Webber</a>, whose lands bordered House Osgrey's. Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a> sent her <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> across the <a href=\"/index.php/Chequy_Water\" title=\"Chequy Water\">Chequy Water</a> to seize Dake and bring him to <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a> for punishment. When Eustace Osgrey arrived at Coldmoat to demand his release, he learned that Dake had been sewn into a sack with rocks, which was sunk in the moat of Coldmoat.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dake&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403165722\nCache expi